snippet.title: Version 4.7 "An Everlasting Dream Intertwined" Trailer | Genshin Impact
snippet.description:
People often feel trapped by the past.
All those unresolved regrets,
And all those unanswered questions.
Perhaps there'll come a day when they'll be set right,
Or maybe they'll just keep playing out in your dreams.

VA:
Navia — Brenna Larsen
Clorinde — Crystal Lee
Wolfy — Stephen Fu
Sethos — Zeno Robinson
Sigewinne — Sarah Williams
Lumine — Sarah Miller-Crews
Dainsleif — Yuri Lowenthal
